{"tid":1132043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】泛民要求約見　林鄭稱若為施壓會面無意義","createTime":"2019-04-30T04:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T11:05:30.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5e23e8ba272d8e6977fd0ba625c011b8513193","tid":1132043,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"對於泛民要求約見特首商討《逃犯條例》，特首林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，如果要求會面的主要目的是要向她施壓撤回修例，這類會面是沒有意義；但如果會面是想鞏固修訂建議，她認為最好的討論場合應是立法會法案委員會，而不是一個與特首的閉門會議。<br />\n<br />\n另外，被問到修例後，前銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基會否被引渡到內地，林鄭月娥拒絕回應個別個案，或作出任何具揣測性和假設性的回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190430/s00001/1556595442149/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%B4%84%E8%A6%8B-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E6%9C%83%E9%9D%A2%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190430%2Fs00001%2F1556595442149%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25B4%2584%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1RAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=6a5ffc34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190430%2Fs00001%2F1556595442149%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25B4%2584%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E